data.description: Only 8 years old! This house is in excellent shape, ready to move in condition and located in a very quiet neighborhood close to great schools, turnpike, I-95 and plenty of shops, supermarkets and 25 minutes to the beach. It offers an open concept living-dining-kitchen. Large ceramic tile in all the house except the two kids bedrooms. Extra large master shower with two shower heads. Nice and large screened terrace and backyard. Stainless steel kitchen appliances. Granite countertop in kitchen and baths. Washer and Dryer do not convey.
